",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/hampton-va/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Hampton dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"$L29\",null,{\"city\":\"Hampton\",\"state\":\"VA\"}]\n17:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"className\":\"city-insights-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{\"parks\":[{\"id\":\"ChIJl-Ikv6SEuokR26uvBGHk5_E\",\"name\":\"Armistead Animal Inn\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Armistead Animal Inn.  What makes this dog facility special is its spacious, friendly, caring. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. spacious indoor play areas This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (757) 723-5118. Visit their website at https://www.armisteadavevet.com/boarding to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"armistead-animal-inn\",\"address\":\"533 N Armistead Ave\",\"street\":\"533 N Armistead Ave\",\"city\":\"Hampton\",\"state\":\"VA\",\"zipCode\":\"23669\",\"full_address\":\"533 N Armistead Ave, Hampton, VA 23669, USA\",\"latitude\":37.0318848,\"longitude\":-76.3550231,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJl-Ikv6SEuokR26uvBGHk5_E\",\"phone\":\"(757) 723-5118\",\"website\":\"https://www.armisteadavevet.com/boarding\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.6,\"reviewCount\":121,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 5